==English==

===Etymology===
perhaps after Henry French of Concord, MA

===Noun===
'''French [[drain]]'''
# A shallow trench, perhaps lined with tile or containing a perforated pipe, backfilled with gravel and then covered over, used to collect and channel runoff water.

